        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31693588/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31693588/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sitaram/" class=" " title="林中人">林中人</a>
                (生命里的艰辛,务必忍耐,保持清净)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31693588">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“开口说话最好是表不及里，深下去，媒体不便，我也没足够的学问和胆量。”

“我知道他们心里欢喜，但总会一脸忧戚对我说：不管怎样，还是少说几句吧。”

</span>
                <p class="pl">
